ABOUT WILD FRONTIER RV RESORT
EEa beautiful resort nestled in ocala, FLorida!
Situated in a serene wooded environment, yet conveniently near Ocala’s bustling shopping district offers you a peaceful atmosphere without compromising convenience. We are just 3 miles from I-75 exit 354, making us a hidden treasure in the woods.
As you arrive, you’ll notice the 10-foot privacy fence that provides a secure and tranquil park. Upon reaching the office and clubhouse, you’ll be greeted by a charming cabin-style building featuring a red roof reminiscent of a Lincoln log cabin. Step inside to discover our fully remodeled bathhouses, conveniently located near the heated pool, which boasts new furniture and umbrella tables—a perfect spot to cool off and soak up the delightful Florida sunshine.
Our laundry room now includes 7 washers (with 3 double-load units) and 8 dryers for your convenience.
We offer a full calendar of activities, such as Bingo, potluck dinners, holiday dances, game nights, movie nights, pizza nights, pool table games, card games, and much more.
Additionally, enjoy our exclusive weekly event, Street Golf, where you can participate in a fun putting course around the block.
Your monthly rent covers: water, sewer, cable, Wi-Fi, and 20/30/50-amp service. Electricity is metered for stays of 1 week or more.
Each site features paved asphalt with grass patios and picnic tables. We provide garbage pickup at your site every day at 10 am. All you need to do is relax and enjoy everything that Wild Frontier has to offer!
